{"tid":1517720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(個人經驗) 對付警察搜屋唔俾拍攝","createTime":"2019-08-30T04:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T04:41:55.000Z","uid":25188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6d64d76355c0dd93d0b01e8c8624178b7eaa16f6","tid":1517720,"uid":25188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:07:58.000Z","msg":"首先要講清楚我嘅經驗唔係俾popo搜過屋 而係我屋企一直有裝閉路電視<br />\n<br />\n我冇俾人搜過所以唔肯定popo係咪真係會收起哂大家d電腦電話又唔俾你影佢 不過我相信 佢地冇野做唔出<br />\n<br />\n但我諗佢地唔會拆埋屋企個閉路電視掛？<br />\n<br />\n我屋企一直都裝左兩個閉路電視<br />\n一個好似以前電腦用嗰d 成粒眼仔咁好明顯擺喺度 不過佢就對正門口 所以如果popo入門要拆都會捕捉到<br />\n另一個喺燈泡度 我都唔知我屋企人喺邊度搵番黎 同燈泡一模一樣樣 只係中間有粒黑色圓點 但佢可以同燈泡一樣扭上去 所以基本上唔會有人知<br />\n<br />\n同埋一般黎講佢係你喺街都可以得閒check下 亦會自動backup 所有連線入去嘅人都睇得番 所以你都可以同朋友傾定好唔好連下對方睇下對方生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人建議大家可以裝下保障自己：<br />\n俾人偷野有得睇下、<br />\n屋企有老人家可以關心下、<br />\n有工人姐姐可以看管下<br />\n<br />\nReally sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"a0e7a620ab5e35052d3c3de7e894c983b3ae35b8","tid":1517720,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8o6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=26f8c5f1\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8o6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=4ff8905d\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8o6aL69TDc1SPH